longBusinessSummary: Fuse Group Holding Inc. provides consulting service to mining industry clients to find acquisition targets. The company was formerly known as Fuse Enterprises Inc. and changed its name to Fuse Group Holding Inc. in May 2019. The company was founded in 2013 and is headquartered in Arcadia, California. Fuse Group Holding Inc. is a subsidiary of Landbond Home Limited.
